name: Losses.01. Giant Panda
description:
Losses... How often we encounter them and how often we do not notice. Losses are large and small, insignificant and critical.
There are losses that you need to talk about, scream at the top of your lungs and try to somehow prevent or even compensate.

I present a 10-piece series on endangered or vulnerable species.

You will see photos with terrible jpeg compression artifacts, because jpeg is a lossy image compression format. Make the loss as visible as possible.
